title: Junior Girl's Preseason All State - Third Team
text:
Junior Girl's Preseason All State - Third Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason girls All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at Class of 2017 and name our third team All State. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! 
Junior Girls Preseason All State - Third Team Sierra Mitchell, Southeast Polk
